Houston, William L'Estrange Eames - Thomas McLean, Joseph Sherrard, John Turnbull Gibb, George 
McGee, Alexander Harrison Dill.

Notes:  There are discrepancies regarding Henderson's exact initials. He was recorded simply 
        "J. Henderson", as "A.W. Henderson" and even "T. Henderson" in various contemporary 
        newspapers and annuals.  
                   


