Referee:   William Finlay (Ireland)
Crowd:     7.500, Underwood Park, Paisley
Goals:     1-0 Wilson (20), 2-0 Paul (36), 3-0 Paul (43), 4-0 Paul (60), 5-0 Paul (70)
