ENGLAND:
William Robert Moon - Arthur Melmoth Walters, Percy Melmoth Walters [c] - George Haworth,
Henry Allen, Alfred Shelton - William Isaiah Bassett, Edmund Samuel Currey, Dr.Tinsley
Lindley, Harry Wood, Harry Butler Daft.

Notes:  This was a World record attendance for a full International match.
        Scotland and England shared the British Home Championship for the 2nd time.                     
        
